      "title": "Management and leadership for nurse administrators",
      "abstract": "Roussel (nursing, University of South Alabama) provides new chapters on total quality management, the theory of human resource development, and collective bargaining in this fourth edition of a text for nurses and nursing students. There is also new material on recommendations from the Institute of Medicine, the Magnet Appraisal process, and ethics"
